    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="hexo-generate-报错"><a href="#hexo-generate-报错" class="headerlink" title="hexo  generate 报错"></a>hexo  generate 报错</h3><p>ERROR Render HTML failed: 2020/05/18/hello-world/index.html<br>TypeError: Cannot read property ‘replace’ of null</p>
<p>不知道啥原因啊。最后重装 next 解决了</p>
]]></content>
